dcterms:description: A large publicly available SMILES dataset with over 1 billion molecules, curated from various datasets such as the ZINC and UniCHEM libraries. It consists of various molecular types ranging from drug-like molecules, peptides, multi-fragment molecules, polymers, reagents, and non-small molecules.
dcterms:title: SAFE dataset

dcterms:creator: J. J. Irwin
B. K. Shoichet
dcterms:description: A dataset comprising 250k small drug-like molecules from the ZINC database, specifically utilized for fine-tuning models to maintain consistency with the MOOD model.
dcterms:title: zinc250k dataset
